<p>
<seg id=1> The ground control persons of hot air balloon trial uninterrupted round-the-world fly said, three pilots on the hot air balloon should fly out of Chinese territorial air space on Wednesday and then fly eastward across Pacific Ocean. </seg>
<seg id=2> On Tuesday, this three-person team encountered political trouble when their hot air balloon deviated from a flight route stipulated by Chinese authority. </seg>
<seg id=3> Chinese officials once ordered them to land on Tibet administered by China. But after some negotiation with British and American foreign affair officials, Chinese side withdrew this command. </seg>
